{"tid":1627464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非和林鄭偽政府割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T19:13:31.000Z","uid":290846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0251ee41c731d9d0edc47032f826116bafcdfc7f","tid":1627464,"uid":290846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"反對反蒙面惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d84ffd19aeaba11c4d80d46950ba1b10eb566e1","tid":1627464,"uid":52468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0251ee41c731d9d0edc47032f826116bafcdfc7f","tid":1627464,"uid":290846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"反對反蒙面惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"不如反對緊急法喇"},{"pid":"760cd7025784d3f6e1740ebaace4ccfbc374c221","tid":1627464,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0251ee41c731d9d0edc47032f826116bafcdfc7f","tid":1627464,"uid":290846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:58:13.000Z","msg":"反對反蒙面惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:13:31.000Z","msg":"<ins>林鄭使用<strong>緊急法</strong>去立<strong>曚面法</strong></ins><br />\n<strong>目的:</strong><br />\n引發更多市民的怒氣, 引起更多人出街<br />\n1, 使政府立緊急法合理化<br />\n2, 繞過正常程序, 為日後透過緊急法立其它法鋪路 (如凍結資產, 限制通訊, 限制外匯)<br />\n3, 以此為藉口, 推遲或取消區議會, 使原本100%己敗的選舉重新定位<br />\n<br />\n<strong>解決方案:</strong><br />\n<strong>1, 拉一派, 打一派</strong>, 儘量透過這次立緊急法同曚面法<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帶來的負面影響</span></strong>争取<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">更多團體的支持</span></strong>, 例如受影響的商家, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標對準林鄭班子</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>2, 敵進我退</strong>, 當我們知道對家的棋路之後, 就要往<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">相反</span></strong>的方向做, 對家期望會更亂, 我地就要更有秩序, 對家想跟我們決一死戰, 我們就要休息<br />\n<strong>3, 虛實並用, 不戰而屈人之兵,</strong> 若一個吹得起既風而鈎到過百隻狗, 最後班狗無功而回, 不費一兵一卒, 一蚊都唔使比。同樣係政治, 經濟, 媒體, 文宣勇武, 和理非各項必須虛實並用, <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標係不戰而屈人之兵, 以小本勝大本, 令對方管治成本大福上升</span></span></strong>, 以消耗他們龐大的資源<br />\n<strong>4, 令對方各員產生<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">恐懼</span></span></strong></strong>, 不論任何方法, 讓敵方望而遠之, 要他們確切知道幫港共政權做事是有很重的代價<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總結: 因時制宜</span></span></strong>"}]}